{"article_id":"LrZxpc1aTsxTaFTV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Attorney General William Barr told a Senate panel Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that he is reviewing","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"whether federal authorities improperly spied on President Donald Trump 's campaign during the early stages of the investigation","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"into whether any of his aides participated in Russian efforts","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"to sway the 2016 election in Trump 's favor .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"`` Spying on a campaign is a big deal , ''","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Barr told a Senate panel Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"spying did occur .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The question is whether it was adequately predicated . ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The attorney general said","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"he planned to examine the `` genesis and the conduct '' of the FBI 's investigation into possible ties between the Trump campaign and Russia ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"launched in the midst of the 2016 presidential run .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"The inquiry was ultimately turned over to special counsel Robert Mueller to complete ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and Barr has said","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"it concluded","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"that Trump 's campaign did not conspire with the Russian government .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"`` I am not saying","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that improper surveillance occurred , ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Barr told the Senate Appropriations subcommittee .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"`` I am concerned about it .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"There is a basis for my concern . ''","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Barr , however , declined to say what specific concern prompted his review","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"or to describe the parts of the investigation","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"he considered to be spying .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Earlier Wednesday , Trump characterized the Mueller investigation as both `` illegal '' and an `` attempted coup , ''","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"while expressing support for a review by Barr .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"`` There is a hunger","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"for this to happen , ''","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Trump told reporters .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"The department 's inspector general is conducting a review of surveillance warrants","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"authorities","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"used","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"to eavesdrop on a former campaign aide , Carter Page , in October 2016 .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Barr has said","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"that effort should be completed by June .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"Republicans in Congress have complained repeatedly","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that the FBI targeted Trump 's campaign for political reasons ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"revealing text messages between two senior officials","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"involved in the probe","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"who expressed their personal contempt for Trump .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"So far , however , investigations in Congress have not produced evidence","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that the extraordinary inquiry","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"into whether Trump 's campaign cooperated with Russian efforts","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"to sway the 2016 election","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"that put him in office","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"were politically motivated or meant to sabotage his campaign .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Among the questions","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Barr said","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"he would seek to answer","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"is why the Trump campaign was not notified in advance by federal authorities of its examination of Russian election interference .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"`` I do n't understand","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"why the campaign was not advised , ''","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Barr said .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Building on his testimony a day earlier before a House committee ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Barr told lawmakers Wednesday","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"that he planned to ask other Justice Department officials to examine","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"whether the department abused its surveillance powers .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"he had not formed a view","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"of whether the department or other intelligence agencies acted improperly ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"but the sensitivity","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"of using national security tools","depth":15},{"id":64,"text":"to investigate the conduct of a political campaign","depth":15},{"id":65,"text":"required scrutiny .","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"Barr said","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"that he did not view surveillance abuse as `` a problem endemic to the FBI , ''","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"but suggested","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that there was likely `` a failure among a group of leaders there . ''","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"The attorney general 's references to possible surveillance abuses came at a crucial time ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"as Barr prepared to release a redacted version of Mueller 's final report on the Russia investigation `` next week . ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Republicans immediately seized on the statements ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"seeking to use them","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to cast the government 's investigation of Russia and the Trump campaign as illegitimate .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"`` Now , the investigation has flipped , ''","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"said Brad Parscale , manager of Trump 's re-election campaign .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"`` This attempted coup needs to be fully investigated . ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Democrats said","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Barr 's choice of words suggested","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"he was courting the favor of a president","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"who has frequently attacked the investigation and the people","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"who conducted it .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif. , said","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Mueller 's assessment of the investigation","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"- not Barr 's -","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"should hold sway .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"`` I do n't trust Barr ;","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"I trust Mueller , ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Pelosi said in an interview with the Associated Press .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Barr , meanwhile , asserted","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"that some parts of Mueller 's report must remain secret","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"because they contain grand jury information , sensitive national security material ,","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"may interfere with ongoing inquiries","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"or contain information","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"that could be damaging to the reputations of those","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"who were not charged in the special counsel 's investigation .","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"The attorney general said","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Mueller and his staff were working","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"to help remove sensitive information from the report","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"so it could be released to Congress and the public .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"And he defended the summary conclusions","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"he delivered to Congress last month","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"and the speed","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"with which those conclusions were made public .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"But lawmakers closely questioned Barr on his decision","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"to release a bare-bones summary of the report last month","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"in which the attorney general said","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Mueller had not found a conspiracy","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"involving the Trump campaign and the Russian government .","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"The special counsel did not make a determination","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"about whether the president 's actions during the investigation amounted to obstruction .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Instead , Barr and his deputy , Rod Rosenstein , separately determined","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"that Trump 's conduct did not constitute a crime .","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"Barr told the Senate on Wednesday","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"that Mueller did not indicate","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"whether he expected Congress to settle the issue of obstruction .","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"Mueller also did not indicate","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"that the decision should be ceded to the attorney general ,","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"Barr said .","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"The attorney general added","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"that he and Rosenstein","depth":16},{"id":122,"text":"- along with other Justice officials -","depth":16},{"id":123,"text":"concluded independently","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"that Trump 's conduct was not criminal .","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"`` I do n't know","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"whether Bob Mueller supported my conclusion , ''","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"Barr said .","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"The attorney general 's intervention at the end of Mueller 's investigation has set off a politically charged battle for access to the entire text of the special counsel 's report , the fruit of a 22-month investigation","depth":5},{"id":129,"text":"that has shadowed the Trump administration since its first days .","depth":5},{"id":130,"text":"While Barr had been called before the Senate and House committees this week","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"to discuss the Justice Department 's $ 29 billion budget ,","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"the focus of both hearings was trained on his handling of Mueller 's report and when the document would be made public .","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"On Tuesday , Barr told the House committee","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"that he had no plans","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"to ask for a court 's permission","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"to disclose grand jury material","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"but said","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"he would consult with Congress","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"after he releases the report","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"to determine","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"whether he can provide additional information .","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"House Democrats vowed last week","depth":6},{"id":143,"text":"that they would seek Mueller 's testimony in addition to that of Barr ,","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"who also is expected to address the matter for congressional committees in early May .","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"Justice , however , has defended Barr 's handling of the report ,","depth":6},{"id":146,"text":"suggesting","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"that the full document was so packed with secret grand jury information","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"that revealing even portions of it immediately would have been impossible .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":297,"left":0,"right":296,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":296,"left":184,"right":295,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":173,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":158,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":153,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":1,"right":152,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":2,"right":151,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":3,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity"